name: Vorka Virus (Final Form)
description:
Vorka Virus finally evolves into something malicious.
Starting as a computer virus, now the AntiMetro can infect humans through smart devices.
It will ruin people's minds, make them addicted to anything meta, cutting real-life connections with other humans.
Without the ability to socialize, commune, and support each other, human civilizations slowly decay.

Featuring the explosion of suffering and destruction by Fabian Winandi.
